PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773176767
OL,3,CBlood test predicts dementia risk in
OL,4,Cwomen 'decades before symptoms appear'
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FDuring the 25 years of follow-up,
OL,12,Fresearchers noted the women who
OL,13,Fdeveloped memory or thinking problems,
OL,14,Fincluding dementia.
OL,16,FThey found that those who had higher
OL,17,Flevels of p-tau217 in their blood at
OL,18,Fthe start of the study were much more
OL,19,Flikely to develop dementia later in
OL,20,Flife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773176767
OL,3,CBlood test predicts dementia risk in
OL,4,Cwomen 'decades before symptoms appear'
OL,6,FAs levels of the biomarker increased,
OL,7,Fso did the risk of dementia, meaning
OL,8,Fthose with the highest levels
OL,9,Fgenerally had the biggest risk.
OL,11,FHowever, the team also found that risk
OL,12,Fwas not the same for everyone, with
OL,13,Ftest differences seen for different
OL,14,Fages of women, ethnicity, hormone
OL,15,Ftherapy (HRT) use and genetic factors
OL,16,Fknown to affect dementia.
OL,18,FThese areas require further research.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
