PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773176767
OL,3,CBlood test predicts dementia risk in
OL,4,Cwomen 'decades before symptoms appear'
OL,6,FDr Sheona Scales, director of research
OL,7,Fat Alzheimer's Research UK, said:
OL,8,F"Women are twice as likely to be
OL,9,Faffected by dementia, but we do not
OL,10,Funderstand why there is this
OL,11,Fdifference.
OL,13,F"This study adds to growing research
OL,14,Fexploring whether bloodbased
OL,15,Fbiomarkers could identify who may be
OL,16,Fat higher risk of dementia decades
OL,17,Fbefore symptoms develop."
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOUyD@YO]
